        "image_with_text_ANbFUr": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "His and hers Promise rings",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>Celebrate the bond of love with our exquisite collection of his and hers couples rings. Each order includes a keepsake Promise Card, allowing you to capture your unique promise and create a lasting memory together. </p><p>Show your commitment to each other with these meaningful rings, symbolising the unbreakable connection you share. </p><p>Whether it's a promise of a lifetime together or a token of your enduring love, these rings are a timeless expression of your devotion. Perfect for commemorating milestones like anniversaries or engagements, they serve as a beautiful reminder of your journey together. So why not exchange vows of love and fidelity with his and hers couples rings, forging an unbreakable bond that will be treasured for years to come?</p>",
            "link_url": "",
