        "richtext_NQCbmi": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A pinky promise is one of the simplest yet most powerful gestures two people can share. When two little fingers link together, it represents a promise built on trust, loyalty and honesty. It is a moment that says “this matters” without needing anything more.<br/><br/>A pinky promise ring takes that fleeting gesture and turns it into something lasting. Instead of a promise that exists only in the moment, the ring becomes a symbol you can wear every day, a quiet reminder of a commitment made between two people.<br/><br/>At The Promise Co, this idea sits at the heart of everything we create. The brand was founded around the meaning of the pinky promise itself, making The Promise Co the original pinky promise ring brand, created to turn that universal gesture of trust into something lasting and meaningful.<br/></p>"
          }
        }
