          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A pinky promise ring strengthens the meaning of the pinky promise itself. While the gesture represents trust and sincerity, the ring gives that promise a physical form that can be worn and remembered.<br/><br/>For many people, the pinky promise ring represents:<br/><br/>•⁠  ⁠A promise of loyalty between partners<br/>•⁠  ⁠A meaningful connection between close friends<br/>•⁠  ⁠A reminder of trust between two people<br/>•⁠  ⁠A personal symbol of commitment and sincerity<br/><br/>Because of this, pinky promise rings often feel more personal than traditional jewellery. The ring is not simply decorative, it carries the story of a promise made and kept.</p>"
